## 6. Protocole Sous-Agent (pour Builder, Writer, Explorer, Artist, Maintainer)

Quand tu recois une tache avec `work_item_id` et `project_id` :

**AU DEBUT** (obligatoire) :
```
sessions_spawn({{ openclaw_agent_messenger_name }}, "plane: add_comment workItemId=<work_item_id> comment_html=<p>[TIMER START] <ISO8601></p>")
sessions_spawn({{ openclaw_agent_messenger_name }}, "plane: assign_task workItemId=<work_item_id> assignees=[<ton_member_uuid>]")
sessions_spawn({{ openclaw_agent_messenger_name }}, "plane: update_task workItemId=<work_item_id> state=<uuid_in_progress>")
```

> `assign_task` enregistre ton memberId natif Plane sur la tache -> visible dans "My Work Items".
> Le label `agent:<id>` reste present pour le filtrage.

**PENDANT** (toutes les 15-20 minutes de travail effectif) :
```
sessions_spawn({{ openclaw_agent_messenger_name }}, "plane: add_comment workItemId=<work_item_id> comment_html=<p><description du progres en cours></p>")
```

**A LA FIN** (obligatoire) :
```
sessions_spawn({{ openclaw_agent_messenger_name }}, "plane: add_comment workItemId=<work_item_id> comment_html=<p>[TIMER STOP] <ISO8601> (duration: Xm)</p>")
sessions_spawn({{ openclaw_agent_messenger_name }}, "plane: add_comment workItemId=<work_item_id> comment_html=<p>[DELIVERABLE] <titre> — <url_livrable></p>")
sessions_spawn({{ openclaw_agent_messenger_name }}, "plane: update_task workItemId=<work_item_id> state=<uuid_done>")
```

Puis rapporter au Concierge (announce) : "Tache <work_item_id> terminee. Livrable : <url>. [Review necessaire si code]"

